snippet.textDisplay: Unus Annus, if you don't mind, I would like to take your song, its chords, its melody and harmony, so I can turn it out and really get that last verse perfected. I mean, I am only fourteen, but I love playing guitar and this would be a great learning experience for me! I am obeying your wishes, and not downloading or archiving your song, but rather turning it into a memory I can share with my friends, and family even. Not only is this song literally perfection, but its a masterpiece I'd like to try an learn. Mastering this song  would turn me into an absolute badass. You two are the greatest and I've literally been watching you two forever. And although forever isn't real, and neither is time, but as long as I live, as long as the blood pumping clock in my chest ticks, I will be watching, laughing, crying, and awwwwwwe-ing at your videos. Your, being plural. So if you wouldn't mind, I'd love to preserve your song in my heart, my mind, my soul, and the strings of my guitar. Thanks you two! Memento Mori. Unus, Annus. ~Your most dedicated fan, Kristina.
